  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the effectiveness of a minimally invasive treatment, consisting of
      partial polymer-infiltrated-ceramic-network (PICN) restorations, used in case of
      rehabilitation of advanced and generalized dental wear over a period of 5 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
